* BMAP phase-2 scanner test fixture  (column-1 '*' = comment)
                first 16 columns blank => this card is a comment
       USE    .MAIN.,1
START  LDA    X+1
       ADA    Y,2
       STA    Z(QU)
       TRA    *+2
COUNT  EQU    5
       BSS    COUNT
       DEC    1,2,3
       OCT    777,0
ARR    BLOCK  DATA,4
       EVEN
       VFD    18/X,18/Y
DONE
       DUP    2,1
       END    START
